    "storyline" => """
      Ala Mhigo is at last free from imperial rule, but that liberty may prove fleeting as the Empire moves to both reclaim this bloodied nation and subjugate all of Eorzea. In their hour of need, however, they cannot turn to the Warrior of Light. Nor to the Scions, who yet slumber, their souls adrift.       """
    "summary" => "SHADOWBRINGERS is the third expansion for FFXIV. The expansion takes players to the First, one of thirteen reflections of the Source that is being consumed by a Flood of Light.
